Music::Canon - utility routines for musical canon construction

To install this module, use CPAN, for example:

  cpanm Music::Canon

For the current release, see:

http://github.com/thrig/Music-Canon

which can be installed by cloning that directory then running `cpanm .`
therein.

DEPENDENCIES

Some knowledge of music theory may well benefit the user. In particular,
"The Technique of Canon" by Hugo Norden, if available, is an excellent
resource on writing canons.

